&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1&quot;&gt;We are looking for people who tailor their approach to our prospects, delivering highly personalized, meticulously researched outreach. &lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;9,1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;136&quot;&gt;And frankly, we expect to see that exact same effort in the way you apply for this role.&lt;/strong&gt; Show us you know how to stand out.&lt;/p&gt;
