&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Wunderkind:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Wunderkind is&amp;nbsp;a performance marketing solution that uses AI and data to help brands acquire and retain customers through one-to-one, personalized messages across websites, email, text, and ads, guaranteeing a lift in revenue.&lt;span data-cid=&quot;2a0c5fb1-1eca-423c-a50e-c44ccd4795c0&quot;&gt; Founded in 2010, &lt;/span&gt;Our goal is to scale a brand’s ability to create and grow customer relationships through websites, email, text, and ads.&amp;nbsp;We believe individuals should have the freedom to choose the kind of internet they want. An internet that fosters genuine relationships with brands. An internet that treats humans like real people instead of “web traffic.”&amp;nbsp;We also believe in empowering brands to treat their customers as individuals, satisfying their unique needs with tailored experiences and thoughtful communication. By expertly personalizing, automating, and scaling beautiful one-to-one experiences, Wunderkind helps brands acquire new customers at scale and keep them loyal for life.&lt;/p&gt;
